{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Chris Anderson: Julian, welcome."},{"time":2000,"text":"It's been reported that WikiLeaks, your baby,"},{"time":4000,"text":"has, in the last few years"},{"time":6000,"text":"has released more classified documents"},{"time":9000,"text":"than the rest of the world's media combined."},{"time":11000,"text":"Can that possibly be true?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":13000,"text":"Julian Assange: Yeah, can it possibly be true?"},{"time":15000,"text":"It's a worry -- isn't it? -- that the rest of the world's media"},{"time":18000,"text":"is doing such a bad job"},{"time":20000,"text":"that a little group of activists"},{"time":22000,"text":"is able to release more"},{"time":24000,"text":"of that type of information"},{"time":26000,"text":"than the rest of the world press combined."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28000,"text":"CA: How does it work?"},{"time":30000,"text":"How do people release the documents?"},{"time":33000,"text":"And how do you secure their privacy?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":36000,"text":"JA: So these are -- as far as we can tell --"},{"time":38000,"text":"classical whistleblowers,"},{"time":40000,"text":"and we have a number of ways for them"},{"time":42000,"text":"to get information to us."},{"time":44000,"text":"So we use this state-of-the-art encryption"},{"time":46000,"text":"to bounce stuff around the Internet, to hide trails,"},{"time":48000,"text":"pass it through legal jurisdictions"},{"time":50000,"text":"like Sweden and Belgium"},{"time":53000,"text":"to enact those legal protections."},{"time":57000,"text":"We get information in the mail,"},{"time":59000,"text":"the regular postal mail,"},{"time":62000,"text":"encrypted or not,"},{"time":64000,"text":"vet it like a regular news organization, format it --"},{"time":67000,"text":"which is sometimes something that's quite hard to do,"},{"time":70000,"text":"when you're talking about"},{"time":72000,"text":"giant databases of information --"},{"time":74000,"text":"release it to the public"},{"time":76000,"text":"and then defend ourselves"},{"time":78000,"text":"against the inevitable legal and political attacks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81000,"text":"CA: So you make an effort to ensure"},{"time":83000,"text":"the documents are legitimate,"},{"time":85000,"text":"but you actually"},{"time":87000,"text":"almost never know who the identity of the source is?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":90000,"text":"JA: That's right, yeah. Very rarely do we ever know,"},{"time":94000,"text":"and if we find out at some stage"},{"time":97000,"text":"then we destroy that information as soon as possible."},{"time":100000,"text":"(Phone ring) God damn it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":106000,"text":"CA: I think that's the CIA asking what the code is"},{"time":108000,"text":"for a TED membership."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":113000,"text":"So let's take [an] example, actually."},{"time":115000,"text":"This is something"},{"time":117000,"text":"you leaked a few years ago."},{"time":119000,"text":"If we can have this document up ..."},{"time":121000,"text":"So this was a story in Kenya a few years ago."},{"time":123000,"text":"Can you tell us what you leaked and what happened?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":126000,"text":"JA: So this is the Kroll Report."},{"time":128000,"text":"This was a secret intelligence report"},{"time":131000,"text":"commissioned by the Kenyan government"},{"time":133000,"text":"after its election in 2004."},{"time":136000,"text":"Prior to 2004, Kenya was ruled"},{"time":138000,"text":"by Daniel arap Moi"},{"time":140000,"text":"for about 18 years."},{"time":142000,"text":"He was a soft dictator of Kenya."},{"time":145000,"text":"And when Kibaki got into power --"},{"time":147000,"text":"through a coalition of forces that were trying"},{"time":149000,"text":"to clean up corruption in Kenya --"},{"time":151000,"text":"they commissioned this report,"},{"time":153000,"text":"spent about two million pounds"},{"time":155000,"text":"on this and an associated report."},{"time":157000,"text":"And then the government sat on it"},{"time":160000,"text":"and used it for political leverage on Moi,"},{"time":162000,"text":"who was the richest man --"},{"time":164000,"text":"still is the richest man -- in Kenya."},{"time":167000,"text":"It's the Holy Grail of Kenyan journalism."},{"time":170000,"text":"So I went there in 2007,"},{"time":173000,"text":"and we managed to get hold of this"},{"time":175000,"text":"just prior to the election --"},{"time":177000,"text":"the national election, December 28."},{"time":182000,"text":"When we released that report,"},{"time":185000,"text":"we did so three days after the new president, Kibaki,"},{"time":188000,"text":"had decided to pal up with"},{"time":190000,"text":"the man that he was going to clean out,"},{"time":192000,"text":"Daniel arap Moi,"},{"time":194000,"text":"so this report then"},{"time":197000,"text":"became a dead albatross"},{"time":199000,"text":"around President Kibaki's neck."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203000,"text":"CA: And -- I mean, to cut a long story short --"},{"time":206000,"text":"word of the report leaked into Kenya,"},{"time":209000,"text":"not from the official media, but indirectly,"},{"time":212000,"text":"and in your opinion, it actually shifted the election."},{"time":215000,"text":"JA: Yeah. So this became front page of the Guardian"},{"time":218000,"text":"and was then printed in all the surrounding countries of Kenya,"},{"time":221000,"text":"in Tanzanian and South African press."},{"time":224000,"text":"And so it came in from the outside."},{"time":226000,"text":"And that, after a couple of days,"},{"time":228000,"text":"made the Kenyan press feel safe to talk about it."},{"time":230000,"text":"And it ran for 20 nights straight on Kenyan TV,"},{"time":233000,"text":"shifted the vote by 10 percent,"},{"time":236000,"text":"according to a Kenyan intelligence report,"},{"time":238000,"text":"which changed the result of the election."}]},{"cues":[{"time":240000,"text":"CA: Wow, so your leak"},{"time":242000,"text":"really substantially changed the world?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":244000,"text":"JA: Yep."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":250000,"text":"CA: Here's -- We're going to just show"},{"time":252000,"text":"a short clip from this"},{"time":255000,"text":"Baghdad airstrike video."},{"time":257000,"text":"The video itself is longer,"},{"time":259000,"text":"but here's a short clip."},{"time":261000,"text":"This is -- this is intense material, I should warn you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264000,"text":"Radio: ... just fuckin', once you get on 'em just open 'em up."},{"time":267000,"text":"I see your element, uh, got about four Humvees, uh, out along ..."},{"time":271000,"text":"You're clear. All right. Firing."},{"time":274000,"text":"Let me know when you've got them. Let's shoot."},{"time":277000,"text":"Light 'em all up."},{"time":279000,"text":"C'mon, fire!"},{"time":281000,"text":"(Machine gun fire)"},{"time":284000,"text":"Keep shoot 'n. Keep shoot 'n."},{"time":287000,"text":"(Machine gun fire)"},{"time":290000,"text":"Keep shoot 'n."},{"time":293000,"text":"Hotel ... Bushmaster Two-Six, Bushmaster Two-Six,"},{"time":295000,"text":"we need to move, time now!"},{"time":297000,"text":"All right, we just engaged all eight individuals."},{"time":300000,"text":"Yeah, we see two birds [helicopters], and we're still firing."},{"time":303000,"text":"Roger. I got 'em."},{"time":305000,"text":"Two-Six, this is Two-Six, we're mobile."},{"time":307000,"text":"Oops, I'm sorry. What was going on?"},{"time":309000,"text":"God damn it, Kyle. All right, hahaha. I hit 'em."}]},{"cues":[{"time":314000,"text":"CA: So, what was the impact of that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":317000,"text":"JA: The impact on the people who worked on it"},{"time":320000,"text":"was severe."},{"time":322000,"text":"We ended up sending two people to Baghdad"},{"time":324000,"text":"to further research that story."},{"time":326000,"text":"So this is just the first of three attacks"},{"time":329000,"text":"that occurred in that scene."}]},{"cues":[{"time":331000,"text":"CA: So, I mean, 11 people died in that attack, right,"},{"time":333000,"text":"including two Reuters employees?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":335000,"text":"JA: Yeah. Two Reuters employees,"},{"time":337000,"text":"two young children were wounded."},{"time":340000,"text":"There were between 18 and 26 people killed all together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":343000,"text":"CA: And releasing this caused"},{"time":345000,"text":"widespread outrage."},{"time":347000,"text":"What was the key element of this"},{"time":349000,"text":"that actually caused the outrage, do you think?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":352000,"text":"JA: I don't know. I guess people can see"},{"time":354000,"text":"the gross disparity in force."},{"time":357000,"text":"You have guys walking in a relaxed way down the street,"},{"time":359000,"text":"and then an Apache helicopter sitting up at one kilometer"},{"time":362000,"text":"firing 30-millimeter cannon shells"},{"time":364000,"text":"on everyone --"},{"time":366000,"text":"looking for any excuse to do so --"},{"time":369000,"text":"and killing people rescuing the wounded."},{"time":371000,"text":"And there was two journalists involved that clearly weren't insurgents"},{"time":374000,"text":"because that's their full-time job."}]},{"cues":[{"time":378000,"text":"CA: I mean, there's been this U.S. intelligence analyst,"},{"time":381000,"text":"Bradley Manning, arrested,"},{"time":383000,"text":"and it's alleged that he confessed in a chat room"},{"time":386000,"text":"to have leaked this video to you,"},{"time":389000,"text":"along with 280,000"},{"time":391000,"text":"classified U.S. embassy cables."},{"time":393000,"text":"I mean, did he?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":396000,"text":"JA: We have denied receiving those cables."},{"time":398000,"text":"He has been charged,"},{"time":400000,"text":"about five days ago,"},{"time":402000,"text":"with obtaining 150,000 cables"},{"time":405000,"text":"and releasing 50."},{"time":407000,"text":"Now, we had released,"},{"time":410000,"text":"early in the year,"},{"time":412000,"text":"a cable from the Reykjavik U.S. embassy,"},{"time":416000,"text":"but this is not necessarily connected."},{"time":418000,"text":"I mean, I was a known visitor of that embassy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":420000,"text":"CA: I mean, if you did receive thousands"},{"time":422000,"text":"of U.S. embassy diplomatic cables ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":425000,"text":"JA: We would have released them. (CA: You would?)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":427000,"text":"JA: Yeah. (CA: Because?)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":430000,"text":"JA: Well, because these sort of things"},{"time":432000,"text":"reveal what the true state"},{"time":435000,"text":"of, say,"},{"time":437000,"text":"Arab governments are like,"},{"time":439000,"text":"the true human-rights abuses in those governments."},{"time":442000,"text":"If you look at declassified cables,"},{"time":444000,"text":"that's the sort of material that's there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":446000,"text":"CA: So let's talk a little more broadly about this."},{"time":448000,"text":"I mean, in general, what's your philosophy?"},{"time":450000,"text":"Why is it right"},{"time":452000,"text":"to encourage leaking of secret information?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":456000,"text":"JA: Well, there's a question as to what sort of information is important in the world,"},{"time":459000,"text":"what sort of information"},{"time":461000,"text":"can achieve reform."},{"time":463000,"text":"And there's a lot of information."},{"time":465000,"text":"So information that organizations"},{"time":467000,"text":"are spending economic effort into concealing,"},{"time":470000,"text":"that's a really good signal"},{"time":472000,"text":"that when the information gets out,"},{"time":474000,"text":"there's a hope of it doing some good --"},{"time":476000,"text":"because the organizations that know it best,"},{"time":478000,"text":"that know it from the inside out,"},{"time":480000,"text":"are spending work to conceal it."},{"time":483000,"text":"And that's what we've found in practice,"},{"time":485000,"text":"and that's what the history of journalism is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":488000,"text":"CA: But are there risks with that,"},{"time":491000,"text":"either to the individuals concerned"},{"time":494000,"text":"or indeed to society at large,"},{"time":496000,"text":"where leaking can actually have"},{"time":498000,"text":"an unintended consequence?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":500000,"text":"JA: Not that we have seen with anything we have released."},{"time":502000,"text":"I mean, we have a harm immunization policy."},{"time":504000,"text":"We have a way of dealing with information"},{"time":506000,"text":"that has sort of personal --"},{"time":508000,"text":"personally identifying information in it."},{"time":511000,"text":"But there are legitimate secrets --"},{"time":514000,"text":"you know, your records with your doctor;"},{"time":517000,"text":"that's a legitimate secret --"},{"time":519000,"text":"but we deal with whistleblowers that are coming forward"},{"time":521000,"text":"that are really sort of well-motivated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":524000,"text":"CA: So they are well-motivated."},{"time":526000,"text":"And what would you say to, for example,"},{"time":528000,"text":"the, you know, the parent of someone"},{"time":531000,"text":"whose son is out serving the U.S. military,"},{"time":534000,"text":"and he says, \"You know what,"},{"time":536000,"text":"you've put up something that someone had an incentive to put out."},{"time":538000,"text":"It shows a U.S. soldier laughing"},{"time":540000,"text":"at people dying."},{"time":542000,"text":"That gives the impression, has given the impression,"},{"time":544000,"text":"to millions of people around the world"},{"time":546000,"text":"that U.S. soldiers are inhuman people."},{"time":548000,"text":"Actually, they're not. My son isn't. How dare you?\""},{"time":550000,"text":"What would you say to that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":552000,"text":"JA: Yeah, we do get a lot of that."},{"time":554000,"text":"But remember, the people in Baghdad,"},{"time":556000,"text":"the people in Iraq, the people in Afghanistan --"},{"time":559000,"text":"they don't need to see the video;"},{"time":561000,"text":"they see it every day."},{"time":563000,"text":"So it's not going to change their opinion. It's not going to change their perception."},{"time":566000,"text":"That's what they see every day."},{"time":568000,"text":"It will change the perception and opinion"},{"time":571000,"text":"of the people who are paying for it all,"},{"time":573000,"text":"and that's our hope."}]},{"cues":[{"time":576000,"text":"CA: So you found a way to shine light"},{"time":579000,"text":"into what you see"},{"time":582000,"text":"as these sort of dark secrets in companies and in government."},{"time":586000,"text":"Light is good."},{"time":588000,"text":"But do you see any irony in the fact that,"},{"time":590000,"text":"in order for you to shine that light,"},{"time":592000,"text":"you have to, yourself,"},{"time":594000,"text":"create secrecy around your sources?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":597000,"text":"JA: Not really. I mean, we don't have"},{"time":600000,"text":"any WikiLeaks dissidents yet."},{"time":604000,"text":"We don't have sources who are dissidents on other sources."},{"time":608000,"text":"Should they come forward, that would be a tricky situation for us,"},{"time":611000,"text":"but we're presumably acting in such a way"},{"time":614000,"text":"that people feel"},{"time":616000,"text":"morally compelled"},{"time":618000,"text":"to continue our mission, not to screw it up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":622000,"text":"CA: I'd actually be interested, just based on what we've heard so far --"},{"time":625000,"text":"I'm curious as to the opinion in the TED audience."},{"time":630000,"text":"You know, there might be a couple of views"},{"time":632000,"text":"of WikiLeaks and of Julian."},{"time":634000,"text":"You know, hero -- people's hero --"},{"time":637000,"text":"bringing this important light."},{"time":640000,"text":"Dangerous troublemaker."},{"time":643000,"text":"Who's got the hero view?"},{"time":647000,"text":"Who's got the dangerous troublemaker view?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":651000,"text":"JA: Oh, come on. There must be some."}]},{"cues":[{"time":654000,"text":"CA: It's a soft crowd, Julian, a soft crowd."},{"time":656000,"text":"We have to try better. Let's show them another example."},{"time":658000,"text":"Now here's something that you haven't yet leaked,"},{"time":661000,"text":"but I think for TED you are."},{"time":664000,"text":"I mean it's an intriguing story that's just happened, right?"},{"time":666000,"text":"What is this?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":668000,"text":"JA: So this is a sample of what we do"},{"time":670000,"text":"sort of every day."},{"time":672000,"text":"So late last year -- in November last year --"},{"time":675000,"text":"there was a series of well blowouts"},{"time":677000,"text":"in Albania,"},{"time":679000,"text":"like the well blowout in the Gulf of Mexico,"},{"time":682000,"text":"but not quite as big."},{"time":684000,"text":"And we got a report --"},{"time":687000,"text":"a sort of engineering analysis into what happened --"},{"time":690000,"text":"saying that, in fact, security guards"},{"time":693000,"text":"from some rival, various competing oil firms"},{"time":696000,"text":"had, in fact, parked trucks there and blown them up."},{"time":700000,"text":"And part of the Albanian government was in this, etc., etc."},{"time":704000,"text":"And the engineering report"},{"time":705000,"text":"had nothing on the top of it,"},{"time":707000,"text":"so it was an extremely difficult document for us."},{"time":709000,"text":"We couldn't verify it because we didn't know"},{"time":711000,"text":"who wrote it and knew what it was about."},{"time":713000,"text":"So we were kind of skeptical that maybe it was"},{"time":715000,"text":"a competing oil firm just sort of playing the issue up."},{"time":717000,"text":"So under that basis, we put it out and said,"},{"time":719000,"text":"\"Look, we're skeptical about this thing."},{"time":721000,"text":"We don't know, but what can we do?"},{"time":723000,"text":"The material looks good, it feels right,"},{"time":725000,"text":"but we just can't verify it.\""},{"time":727000,"text":"And we then got a letter"},{"time":730000,"text":"just this week"},{"time":733000,"text":"from the company who wrote it,"},{"time":736000,"text":"wanting to track down the source --"},{"time":739000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":743000,"text":"saying, \"Hey, we want to track down the source.\""},{"time":746000,"text":"And we were like, \"Oh, tell us more."},{"time":748000,"text":"What document is it, precisely, you're talking about?"},{"time":751000,"text":"Can you show that you had legal authority over that document?"},{"time":754000,"text":"Is it really yours?\""},{"time":756000,"text":"So they sent us this screen shot"},{"time":759000,"text":"with the author"},{"time":761000,"text":"in the Microsoft Word ID."},{"time":766000,"text":"Yeah."},{"time":768000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":773000,"text":"That's happened quite a lot though."},{"time":775000,"text":"This is like one of our methods"},{"time":777000,"text":"of identifying, of verifying, what a material is,"},{"time":780000,"text":"is to try and get these guys to write letters."}]},{"cues":[{"time":782000,"text":"CA: Yeah. Have you had information"},{"time":785000,"text":"from inside BP?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":787000,"text":"JA: Yeah, we have a lot, but I mean, at the moment,"},{"time":790000,"text":"we are undergoing a sort of serious fundraising and engineering effort."},{"time":793000,"text":"So our publication rate"},{"time":795000,"text":"over the past few months"},{"time":797000,"text":"has been sort of minimized"},{"time":799000,"text":"while we're re-engineering our back systems"},{"time":802000,"text":"for the phenomenal public interest that we have."},{"time":805000,"text":"That's a problem."},{"time":807000,"text":"I mean, like any sort of growing startup organization,"},{"time":810000,"text":"we are sort of overwhelmed"},{"time":812000,"text":"by our growth,"},{"time":814000,"text":"and that means we're getting enormous quantity"},{"time":816000,"text":"of whistleblower disclosures"},{"time":818000,"text":"of a very high caliber"},{"time":820000,"text":"but don't have enough people to actually"},{"time":822000,"text":"process and vet this information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":824000,"text":"CA: So that's the key bottleneck,"},{"time":826000,"text":"basically journalistic volunteers"},{"time":828000,"text":"and/or the funding of journalistic salaries?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":831000,"text":"JA: Yep. Yeah, and trusted people."},{"time":833000,"text":"I mean, we're an organization"},{"time":835000,"text":"that is hard to grow very quickly"},{"time":837000,"text":"because of the sort of material we deal with,"},{"time":839000,"text":"so we have to restructure"},{"time":842000,"text":"in order to have people"},{"time":844000,"text":"who will deal with the highest national security stuff,"},{"time":847000,"text":"and then lower security cases."}]},{"cues":[{"time":849000,"text":"CA: So help us understand a bit about you personally"},{"time":852000,"text":"and how you came to do this."},{"time":854000,"text":"And I think I read that as a kid"},{"time":856000,"text":"you went to 37 different schools."},{"time":859000,"text":"Can that be right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":861000,"text":"JA: Well, my parents were in the movie business"},{"time":864000,"text":"and then on the run from a cult,"},{"time":866000,"text":"so the combination between the two ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":868000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":872000,"text":"CA: I mean, a psychologist might say"},{"time":874000,"text":"that's a recipe for breeding paranoia."}]},{"cues":[{"time":877000,"text":"JA: What, the movie business?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":879000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":882000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":885000,"text":"CA: And you were also -- I mean,"},{"time":887000,"text":"you were also a hacker at an early age"},{"time":889000,"text":"and ran into the authorities early on."},{"time":892000,"text":"JA: Well, I was a journalist."},{"time":895000,"text":"You know, I was a very young journalist activist at an early age."},{"time":897000,"text":"I wrote a magazine,"},{"time":899000,"text":"was prosecuted for it when I was a teenager."},{"time":902000,"text":"So you have to be careful with hacker."},{"time":904000,"text":"I mean there's like -- there's a method"},{"time":906000,"text":"that can be deployed for various things."},{"time":908000,"text":"Unfortunately, at the moment,"},{"time":910000,"text":"it's mostly deployed by the Russian mafia"},{"time":912000,"text":"in order to steal your grandmother's bank accounts."},{"time":914000,"text":"So this phrase is not,"},{"time":917000,"text":"not as nice as it used to be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":919000,"text":"CA: Yeah, well, I certainly don't think"},{"time":921000,"text":"you're stealing anyone's grandmother's bank account,"},{"time":924000,"text":"but what about"},{"time":926000,"text":"your core values?"},{"time":928000,"text":"Can you give us a sense of what they are"},{"time":931000,"text":"and maybe some incident in your life"},{"time":933000,"text":"that helped determine them?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":938000,"text":"JA: I'm not sure about the incident."},{"time":940000,"text":"But the core values:"},{"time":943000,"text":"well, capable, generous men"},{"time":946000,"text":"do not create victims;"},{"time":948000,"text":"they nurture victims."},{"time":950000,"text":"And that's something from my father"},{"time":952000,"text":"and something from other capable, generous men"},{"time":955000,"text":"that have been in my life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":958000,"text":"CA: Capable, generous men do not create victims;"},{"time":960000,"text":"they nurture victims?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":962000,"text":"JA: Yeah. And you know,"},{"time":964000,"text":"I'm a combative person,"},{"time":968000,"text":"so I'm not actually so big on the nurture,"},{"time":970000,"text":"but some way --"},{"time":973000,"text":"there is another way of nurturing victims,"},{"time":976000,"text":"which is to police perpetrators"},{"time":979000,"text":"of crime."},{"time":981000,"text":"And so that is something"},{"time":983000,"text":"that has been in my character"},{"time":985000,"text":"for a long time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":987000,"text":"CA: So just tell us, very quickly in the last minute, the story:"},{"time":990000,"text":"what happened in Iceland?"},{"time":993000,"text":"You basically published something there,"},{"time":996000,"text":"ran into trouble with a bank,"},{"time":999000,"text":"then the news service there"},{"time":1001000,"text":"was injuncted from running the story."},{"time":1004000,"text":"Instead, they publicized your side."},{"time":1006000,"text":"That made you very high-profile in Iceland. What happened next?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1009000,"text":"JA: Yeah, this is a great case, you know."},{"time":1011000,"text":"Iceland went through this financial crisis."},{"time":1013000,"text":"It was the hardest hit of any country in the world."},{"time":1015000,"text":"Its banking sector was 10 times the GDP"},{"time":1017000,"text":"of the rest of the economy."},{"time":1019000,"text":"Anyway, so we release this report"},{"time":1022000,"text":"in July last year."},{"time":1025000,"text":"And the national TV station was injuncted"},{"time":1027000,"text":"five minutes before it went on air,"},{"time":1029000,"text":"like out of a movie: injunction landed on the news desk,"},{"time":1031000,"text":"and the news reader was like,"},{"time":1033000,"text":"\"This has never happened before. What do we do?\""},{"time":1035000,"text":"Well, we just show the website instead,"},{"time":1037000,"text":"for all that time, as a filler,"},{"time":1040000,"text":"and we became very famous in Iceland,"},{"time":1042000,"text":"went to Iceland and spoke about this issue."},{"time":1045000,"text":"And there was a feeling in the community"},{"time":1047000,"text":"that that should never happen again,"},{"time":1049000,"text":"and as a result,"},{"time":1051000,"text":"working with Icelandic politicians"},{"time":1053000,"text":"and some other international legal experts,"},{"time":1055000,"text":"we put together a new sort of"},{"time":1057000,"text":"package of legislation for Iceland"},{"time":1060000,"text":"to sort of become an offshore haven"},{"time":1063000,"text":"for the free press,"},{"time":1066000,"text":"with the strongest journalistic protections in the world,"},{"time":1069000,"text":"with a new Nobel Prize"},{"time":1071000,"text":"for freedom of speech."},{"time":1073000,"text":"Iceland's a Nordic country,"},{"time":1075000,"text":"so, like Norway, it's able to tap into the system."},{"time":1078000,"text":"And just a month ago,"},{"time":1080000,"text":"this was passed by the Icelandic parliament unanimously."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1083000,"text":"CA: Wow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1085000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1091000,"text":"Last question, Julian."},{"time":1093000,"text":"When you think of the future then,"},{"time":1095000,"text":"do you think it's more likely to be"},{"time":1097000,"text":"Big Brother exerting more control,"},{"time":1099000,"text":"more secrecy,"},{"time":1101000,"text":"or us watching"},{"time":1103000,"text":"Big Brother,"},{"time":1105000,"text":"or it's just all to be played for either way?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1108000,"text":"JA: I'm not sure which way it's going to go."},{"time":1110000,"text":"I mean, there's enormous pressures"},{"time":1112000,"text":"to harmonize freedom of speech legislation"},{"time":1115000,"text":"and transparency legislation around the world --"},{"time":1118000,"text":"within the E.U.,"},{"time":1120000,"text":"between China and the United States."},{"time":1122000,"text":"Which way is it going to go? It's hard to see."},{"time":1125000,"text":"That's why it's a very interesting time to be in --"},{"time":1127000,"text":"because with just a little bit of effort,"},{"time":1129000,"text":"we can shift it one way or the other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1132000,"text":"CA: Well, it looks like I'm reflecting the audience's opinion"},{"time":1135000,"text":"to say, Julian, be careful,"},{"time":1137000,"text":"and all power to you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1139000,"text":"JA: Thank you, Chris. (CA: Thank you.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1141000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}